{"word":"G2023 - ἐπιχορηγέω - epichorēgéō - ep-ee-khor-ayg-eh'-o - Add","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιχορηγέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epichorēgéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-khor-ayg-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Add</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அளி, வர்த்திக்கச்செய், வளர்ந்தேறு, கூட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to supply, furnish, present"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5524 - χορηγέω - chorēgéō - khor-ayg-eh'-o/5524\">G5524</a>; to <i>furnish besides</i>, that is, fully <i>supply</i>, (figuratively) <i>aid</i> or <i>contribute:</i> - add, minister (nourishment, unto).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}